tip.text: Great Ramen. Mostly crowded and there is a queue. Let them sit you on the bar and watch the chefs create delicious food for you.

They gave me the wrong menu. After 20 mins discovered that it was the wrong menu. The soup was microwave hot. Instead of using napkins they use hand cutted old menus under the bowl. Interesting place.
Well, there are some steaks, burgers and belgian beers. But the service sucks so bad, I never could enjoy this place. They kept giving free stuff like drinks after delays but still, i would skip it.
Beer and water 9.50! Just do not go there.
The best pulpo in town. Period.
